profileInfo:
Standard

  • CDC HL7 Version 2.5.1 Implementation Guide for Immunization Messaging - Release 1.5 (10/01/2014)
  • Immunization Clarification Addendum - 07/2015

Profiles

  • Z22(VXU)- Send Immunization
  • Z23(ACK)- Acknowledgement
  • Z34(QBP)- Query: Complete Immunization History
  • Z44(QBP)- Query: Evaluated Immunization History And Forecast
  • Z31(RSP)- Response: List Of Candidates Profile
  • Z32(RSP)- Response: Complete Immunization History
  • Z33(RSP)- Response: Acknowledgement With No Person Records
  • Z42(RSP)- Response: Evaluated History AND Forecast

Pairs

  • Z22:Z23 - Send Immunization/ACK
  • Z34:Z31 - Query History/Respond Candidates
  • Z34:Z32 - Query History/Respond History
  • Z34:Z33 - Query History/Respond Person Not Found
  • Z34:Z33 - Query History/Respond Too many matches Found
  • Z34:Z23 - Query History/Respond ACK error
  • Z34:Z33 - Query History/Respond Not well formed/fatal errors Found
  • Z44:Z42 - Query History & Forecast/Respond History & Forecast
  • Z44:Z33 - Query History & Forecast/Respond Person Not Found
  • Z44:Z33 - Query History & Forecast/ Respond Too many matches Found
  • Z44:Z33 - Query History & Forecast/ No Immunization history is returned
  • Z44:Z33 - Query History & Forecast/Respond Not well formed/fatal errors Found
  • Z44:Z23 - Query History & Forecast/ Respond ACK error
